2. InitialValue prop initializes the state: `useState(InitialValue ?? "")`
3. OnSave passes `Value` (NOT `Value.trim()`)
4. The submit guard still checks `Value.trim()` for the disabled state and submit handler (empty-after-trim means no submit)

